OL,3,CMan who died after skydive named by
OL,4,Cpolice
OL,6,FA 49-year-old man who died following a
OL,7,Fskydive in Devon has been named by
OL,8,Fpolice.
OL,10,FChas McNeil, from Poole, Dorset, was
OL,11,Fpronounced dead at Dunkeswell
OL,12,FAerodrome near Honiton on 28 February.
OL,14,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,15,Fsite just before 1pm due to concerns
OL,16,Ffor the welfare of a male skydiver.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
