CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1772572325
OL,3,CMan who died after skydive named by
OL,4,Cpolice
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Devon and Cornwall
OL,7,FPolice said: "Mr McNeil, who was from
OL,8,FPoole, was confirmed deceased at the
OL,9,Fscene. His family were informed, and
OL,10,Fwe ask that their privacy is respected.
OL,12,F"Enquiries remain ongoing by police,
OL,13,FBritish Skydiving and East Devon
OL,14,FDistrict Council Environmental Health
OL,15,Fand Safety Office."
OL,17,FThe force added that Mr McNeil's
OL,18,Ffamily had said: "Keep your chin up
OL,19,Fand when you look up at the sky, think
OL,20,Fof Chas."
OL,26,@oD@NOUtD@AOUzD@ROU
