CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1772572325
OL,3,CMan who died after skydive named by
OL,4,Cpolice
OL,6,FSkydive South West, which operates out
OL,7,Fof the aerodrome, previously said Mr
OL,8,FMcNeil had been carrying out a jump
OL,9,Fwith a friend.
OL,11,FIn a statement posted on social media,
OL,12,Fthe centre said: "We are deeply
OL,13,Fsaddened to confirm that an
OL,14,Fexperienced licensed skydiver and
OL,15,Fwingsuit coach with over 10,000 jumps
OL,16,Flogged tragically lost their life
OL,17,Fwhilst carrying out a wingsuit jump
OL,18,Fwith a friend, using his personal
OL,19,Fparachute equipment and an advanced
OL,20,Fwingsuit.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1772572325
OL,3,CMan who died after skydive named by
OL,4,Cpolice
OL,6,F"Our thoughts and heartfelt
OL,7,Fcondolences are with their family,
OL,8,Ffriends and the wider skydiving
OL,9,Fcommunity at this incredibly difficult
OL,10,Ftime.
OL,12,F"The club, as required by all clubs
OL,13,Faffiliated to the governing body
OL,14,FBritish Skydiving, followed set
OL,15,Fprocedures by contacting the police
OL,16,Fand British Skydiving so they could
OL,17,Fcarry out their independent
OL,18,Finvestigation as to the cause of the
OL,19,Faccident.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
