OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1772572325
OL,3,CMan who died after skydive named by
OL,4,Cpolice
OL,6,F"Our staff continue to assist British
OL,7,FSkydiving and Devon and Cornwall
OL,8,FPolice, providing all the information
OL,9,Fthey require."
OL,11,FThe incident comes less than a year
OL,12,Fafter two people died while taking
OL,13,Fpart in a tandem jump at the same
OL,14,Fairfield.
OL,16,FSkydiving instructor Adam Harrison,
OL,17,F30, and Belinda Taylor, 48, who was
OL,18,Fstrapped to him, died while skydiving
OL,19,Fin the area of Dunkeswell Aerodrome on
OL,20,F13 June 2025.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
